# HexAstral API (hexastral-api) Development Rules

**Loaded automatically when working under `apps/hexastral-api/`. Overrides root rules.**

---

## 1. Quick Facts

| Dimension | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| **Framework** | Hono 4.9+ |
| **Runtime** | Cloudflare Workers |
| **Database** | D1 (SQLite) + Drizzle ORM |
| **Validation** | Zod v4 + @hono/zod-validator |
| **Auth** | HMAC (iOS) or Turnstile (Web) |
| **Deploy** | wrangler deploy |
| **Local Port** | 3010 |

---

## 2. Forbidden Patterns ❌

| Forbidden | Why | Alternative |
|-----------|-----|-------------|
| Direct `c.env.SVC_*` calls | No timeout, inconsistent error handling | `lib/service-clients.ts` |
| Mixed auth middleware | Security hole | Route: HMAC XOR Turnstile only |
| Empty `catch {}` | Swallows errors | `logger.error(...)` or rethrow |
| Direct DB field assign | Race conditions | `db.batch([...])` atomic ops |
| N+1 queries | Poor performance | Relational `with: { ... }` |
| Vague error responses | Hard to debug | `HTTPException(status, { message })` |
| `any` or `as Type` | Type loss | Zod parse or type guards |

---

## 3. Project Structure

```
src/
├── index.ts              # Entry + onError
├── types.ts              # Global types
├── infra-types.ts        # Cloudflare bindings
├── db/schema.ts          # Drizzle tables (single source of truth)
├── middleware/
│   ├── hmac-verify.ts    # iOS auth
│   ├── turnstile-verify.ts # Web auth
│   ├── db-middleware.ts   # DB injection
│   └── logging.ts        # Request logging
├── lib/
│   ├── service-clients.ts # Microservice calls
│   └── validators.ts     # Shared Zod schemas
├── routes/               # Route handlers
└── services/             # Business logic
```

