## 10. Logging & Tracing

```typescript
import { createLogger } from '@zhop/logger'

const logger = createLogger('hexastral-api')

// ✅ Structured logging
logger.error('Chart computation failed', {
  requestId: c.get('requestId'),
  userId: c.get('userId'),
  chartType: 'bazi',
  error: err instanceof Error ? err.message : String(err),
})

// ❌ Don't
console.log('Error:', err)  // loses structured context
```

