## 11. Wrangler & scripts (hexastral-api)

- **Always** `bunx wrangler …` from **`apps/hexastral-api`** (this package’s devDependency). Do not assume global `wrangler` has `ai-search` or current config schema.
- **Prefer** `package.json` scripts: `bun dev`, `bun deploy`, `bun db:generate`, `bun db:migrate`, `bun db:migrate:prod`, `bun run ai-search:info`, `bun cf-typegen`.
- **After** `wrangler.jsonc` edits: `bunx wrangler types` (or `bun cf-typegen`).
- **AI Search binding**: `ai_search[].instance_name` === API instance **`id`**.
- D1/KV/tail/deployments flags: use **Wrangler skill** / **cloudflare-docs** MCP — do not duplicate long command lists here.

---

## 12. Deploy Checklist

- [ ] `bun typecheck` passes
- [ ] `bun db:generate` run (if schema changed)
- [ ] Local test passes (`bun dev`)
- [ ] Migration SQL reviewed (`cat migrations/...`)
- [ ] Secrets set (`bunx wrangler secret put …` as needed)
- [ ] No `console.log` / `// @ts-ignore`
- [ ] All routes have auth middleware
- [ ] Error handling complete (no empty catch)

```bash
bun deploy
# Optional: bunx wrangler deployments list hexastral-api
# Optional: bunx wrangler rollback hexastral-api
```

